	(text_box "About:\n- STM32L43 MCU is system brain\n\nFunctionalities: \n- Configure and reads data from ADC (ADS131M08)\n- Controls balancer FETs\n- Controls main switch (TPS1200)\n- Reads battery NTC\n- Stores battery data into EEPROM\n- Handles user communication I2C and CAN\n- Provides UART debug communication"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
